60bc987b8e0b1bc49eef7a3473f2673707b6270","tid":1774202,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"出緊嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15d1c71204b5dee801318b67048d1ee232c4e53","tid":1774202,"uid":265257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c450c401a999cff13e653a606b217a89a7ccfb2f","tid":1774202,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T05:59:58.000Z","msg":"今日係咪有得睇某位巴打食屎魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:19:52.000Z","msg":"推返佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426780e98809cbe9df2b87184e6368efa8c13d82","tid":1774202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191208/60355064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191208%2F60355064&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekcwmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=06b8b78c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191208%2F60355064&h=9f6fcd72\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191208/60355064</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】12.8遊行前 警方西隧口設路障查車 過港島現車龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191208/large/1575782957_1154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191208%2Flarge%2F1575782957_1154.jpg&h=4692dcd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 現場6條行車線，封了5條線，只剩下1條行車線供車輛經過。張培生攝<br />\n<br />\n民陣今日發起「國際人權日遊行」，是近4個月來首獲警方發出不反對通知書，網民都號召「和理非」再次走出來。中午12時許，警方在西區海底隧道往港島方向的西九龍入口附近設置路障，檢查路經的車輛，導致現場交通一度大擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【理大圍城】拒做冷氣軍師偕義工組隊「洗樓執仔」 朱偉志：每日都擔心有冇人死<br />\n<br />\n西隧往港島方向的西九龍入口，中午12時許，警方在圓方對開附近設置路障，現場6條行車線，封了5條線，只剩下1條行車線供車輛經過，導致西九龍公路出現車龍，交通擠塞。警方以雪糕筒架設路障，現場至少停泊了兩輛警車及兩輛旅遊巴。<br />\n另外，東區走廊往銅鑼灣方向，亦有警員設置路障檢查駛經車輛；大欖隧道轉車站出市區方向，有大批防暴警員把守，並登上出市區的巴士檢查。而在大埔廣福邨，亦有便衣探員登上巴士搜查。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【理大圍城】校長奔赴現場只為「敲得開對門」 葉建源：所有學生都係我嘅學生"},{"pid":"7096246f766b093adde5b2c7c2c5fb46863e8599","tid":1774202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnFucvM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnFucvM.jpg&h=0f4d4d81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d998075623c875cc91b9a63d33fe7469b814e","tid":1774202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/12/08/145251_ed5ec89f87a89a8913e3adab7948bb70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F12%2F08%2F145251_ed5ec89f87a89a8913e3adab7948bb70.jpg&h=2b681b64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b10042434e8424cb198fbdb65067a1c99b0de8c1","tid":1774202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"排緊隊出維園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwamN95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwamN95.jpg&h=9c520c36&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KpbqWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KpbqWU.jpg&h=a9f951e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a43b64a1a16bcce7c51c839c372d845ffa93d6aa","tid":1774202,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"排緊隊出維園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gwamN95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgwamN95.jpg&h=9c520c36&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KpbqWU.jpg\" data-thumbnai